title: The Chaff
description: In an effort to get Teen Titan Go! canceled, Control Freak shows off some deleted scenes.

title: Vote Por Zombozo
description: Cuando el Chatarra debe ponerse a punto en la misma ciudad por donde pasa la campaña de Zombozo, Ben pronto descubre que el payaso usa sus discursos para hipnotizar al pueblo y robarse sus pertenencias. El equipo Tennyson debe impedir que el villano gane las elecciones.

title: El dia divertido de Falafel
description: Cuando Falafel decide empacar sus cosas e ir a la ciudad, Manzana y Cebollín deben convencerlo de quedarse.

title: Portal hacia Helen
description: Craig hace una conexión a larga distancia con un niño que ama el Arroyo tanto como él.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Pajama Pajimjams
description: Oscar pretends to be a talking pair of pajamas named "Jimjams" to make his friend Pajamas happy.

title: Bring Out Your Beast
description: Craig wants to play a popular card game, so he decides to borrow Bernard's vintage and valuable cards.

title: Welcome to Zombozo-Zone!
description: During medieval times, Team Tennyson must fight to remember that they're not in the past at all, but actually at a Renaissance-esque faire, where "King Zombozo" has hypnotized its guests into thinking they live in the past!

title: Dinner at the Creek
description: Bernard is left in charge for the evening, so Craig sets out to find his own dinner at the creek.

title: La Suciedad
description: A Ben le encargan la tarea de limpiar la Chatarra, pero cuando, engañado por los viles villanos Fly Guys, permite que se lo roben, debe perseguirlos antes de que fabriquen una larva monstruosa imparable con un objetivo claro: destruir Las Vegas.

title: De regreso a la guarderia
description: Steven, Amatista y Peridot intentan embellecer la guardería.

title: The Nom Nom Show
description: Things go awry while Nom Nom shoots his first television show. The Bears offer to help and appear on the show.

title: Shmorby
description: The Bears get a Shmorby home assistant device and become lazy couch potatoes.

title: The Pressure
description: Gumball tries to save Darwin from being kissed by a girl.

title: Bear Flu
description: The Bears become terribly ill and Chloe takes it upon herself to take care of them. But things get tricky when word of the Bears' sickness goes viral.

title: Bearz II Men
description: The Baby Bears help a teenager accomplish his dream of being a famous singer.

title: Kelsey Quest
description: Kelsey accepts a quest from the Elders of the Creek, but is she ready for her terrifying opponent?

title: Toma 10
description: Mientras Ben intenta rodar su propia película independiente, por accidente libera a una pandilla de insectos y, cuando la lucha se traslada a su guarida oculta, Ben debe enfrentarse a su líder narcisista: La Hormiga Reina.

title: Ant We All Just Get Along
description: Owen and Beth try to save an ant hill that Courtney and Leshawna want to destroy.

title: Part 1 - Legacy
description: Nya helps Zane backup memories of their adventures to the Samurai X Cave computer, but Zane encounters a mysterious puzzle buried deep within his code.

title: Time Share
description: Batman and Blue Beetle have to travel back in time to stop Chronos from destroying a young Dark Knight on his very first case.

title: Change Your Mind
description: Steven faces his biggest challenge yet.

title: Terminal Velocity Part 1
description: While Windblade is away on a mission, Bee decides to relive a fun memory.

title: Off Colors
description: Steven finds some unusual new allies.

title: Coffee Cave
description: After finding out Ice Bear is a master barista, the Bears turn their cave into a popular coffee shop. But it all goes awry when Ice Bear gets too into coffee and goes berserk.

title: Mama a la Orden
description: Con el deseo de tener la experiencia de una madre, los osos usan una aplicación que les traerá una madre a la puerta de sus casas.

title: Hoyo En 10
description: Mientras Ben juega al minigolf, lo atacan los Ground Hawgs, una pandilla de mutantes convertidos en ciclistas del Doctor Ánimo. Pero cuando los Hawgs se dan cuenta de que la falsa aldea de minigolf no es un lugar real, Ben debe transformarse en alienígena para detenerlos antes de que elijan la ciudad verdadera que está a pocos metros de allí como su blanco.

title: Palomas
description: Grizz se hace muy amigo de una bandada de palomas.

title: The Bluster Bunch
description: A trail of tornadic destruction leads Mega Man, Suna, and Rush through a series of encounters with Air Man's quirky siblings.

title: Itch to Explore
description: Craig's quest to map the entire Creek takes him and his friends into the treacherous Poison Ivy Grove.

title: Snots Landing
description: Beth gets Courtney's diorama furniture stuck up her nose and Courtney needs it back before the diorama contest judge arrives.

title: Familiar
description: With many changes going on in his life, Steven tries to find his place in the world.

title: Saving Faith
description: Lloyd and his team plot to take control of the Oni Titan. Meanwhile in the First Realm, the Ninja fall into Iron Baron's clutches and an old master returns.

title: Shhh!
description: While chilling at a monastery with a no-noise policy, Ben can't keep quiet and accidentally awakens a dangerous Dragon hidden in a secret chamber below the hallowed halls. A job that might be too much for even Diamondhead to handle.

title: Los Supervillanso se Unen
description: Después de una pausa en las payasadas alienígenas, un inquieto Ben les sugiere a Max y Gwen que podría ser un mejor héroe si fuera solo. Pero cuando Vilgax consigue la ayuda de Zombozo para construir un mecanismo hipnotizador gigante para hipnotizar al mundo entero, Ben debe replantearse su estrategia si quiere derrotar al equipo de supervillanos.

title: Zombie King
description: Grundy escapes his Louisiana prison intent on using a magical crystal which will allow him to raise the dead from their graves. Only Batman and Swamp thing stand in the way of his growing zombie army.

title: Out to Launch
description: While on a visit to Cape Canaveral, the Tennyson Trio are present for the inaugural launch of an experimental space plane. When Vilgax commandeers the ship, Ben must stop the baddie from weaponizing the shuttle before the countdown hits zero.

title: Moon Problems
description: The Moon gets sad when Oscar loses his friendship bracelet.

title: Past Aliens Present
description: After Ben stumbles upon a video of Cannonbolt ripping up a computer lab on the internet, Team Tennyson must race to State U to find the imposter; but once Ben discovers it is a steam-punk version of his alien that is terrorizing the campus, Ben must take down the man behind the machine, Steam Smythe!

title: The Job
description: Dad gets his first job as a pizza delivery guy, which rocks the very fabric of the universe.

title: Animo Farm
description: Ben stumbles into Dr. Animo's secret lab now ruled by his superior mutants, the Alphas, and must help the lesser animals escape while stuck as Stinkfly.

title: Sick as a Bot
description: After the Energon seeking WINGCODE infects the Autobots with a virus, Bulkhead joins Grimlock in his frantic hunt for the Decepticon. But to capture the 'Con, the duo of brawny Bots has to learn to keep their cool and come up with a workable plan.

title: Drilling Deep
description: At school, Aki struggles with the side effects of his newly replicated Drill Man schematics; later, as Mega Man, he learns to control his Fire Powers in thwarting Drill Man's assault on Skyraisers Inc.

title: Clown College
description: While tailgating at a State U. homecoming football game, Ben teams up with Grandpa Max's old college buddies to keep the crazy clown Zombozo from robbing the stadium blind at halftime.

title: The Future is Cardboard
description: The kids meet an eccentric Cardboard Creator that invites Craig to help finish his masterpiece.

title: Alone Quest
description: Craig has an "emergency" leaving Kelsey alone at the Stump.

title: Beehive
description: The Bears allow bees to live in the cave to make honey. But soon the Bears, entranced by the honey, become the bees' mindless servants.

title: Aquarium for a Dream
description: Gwen tries to convince Chef to tell the class the truth about their pet goldfish.

title: Yo soy Polar
description: Cuando Polar se golpea la cabeza, Pardo y Panda se dan cuenta de que su comportamiento cambia.

title: The Metric System vs. Freedom
description: Robin teaches the other Titans about the difference between the Imperial System and the Metric System.

title: La prueba
description: Steven va a juicio.

title: Escandalosos
description: Los Osos bebé se inscriben en un torneo de lucha libre mexicana.

title: The Gilded Path
description: The headquarters to the resistance is breached and Lloyd scrambles to avoid capture. Meanwhile, the Ninja are caught by Heavy Metal, but find an unlikely ally.

title: Gemacaciones
description: Greg y las Gemas llevan a Steven de vacaciones para ayudarlo a relajarse.

title: El regreso de Xingo
description: Cuando Ben debe divertirse solo durante la merecida siesta de Max, se topa con un juego de Xingo y decide convertirse en OE-Shock Rock para encenderlo. Pero cuando Xingo recibe demasiada carga, salta al mundo real, y nuestro héroe debe quedar frente a frente con su personaje animado favorito.

title: The 11th Alien Part 2
description: After discovering that Vilgax has joined forces with the Weatherheads to trick him into turning over the Omnitrix, Ben must not only overcome his doubts, but fully embrace his new powers if he is to beat his foes.

title: Reststop Roustabout
description: With the Rustbucket stopped on the Midwest roadside, Ben locks himself inside with his tablet as Max and Gwen enjoy the great outdoors, until Team Tennyson is pulled into a wild Jack-a-Lope chase.

title: Part 3 - Legendary Places
description: Cole joins Jay and Zane inside the Nindroid to solve a mysterious puzzle by revisiting some of Ninjago's distinctive destinations.

title: Bucketboy!
description: When the girls tell Barry he's a hero, he takes it too far.

title: La Invitacion
description: Craig y sus amigos están invitados a una exclusiva merienda con deliciosos postres, si es que pueden quedarse hasta el final de la fiesta.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Classic Rock
description: Batman thinks he's helping a homeless old man who is being mugged on the street only to discover that the man is a powerful wizard being chased by demons in disguise. It turns out the wizard is on a mission to save Shazam from the clutches of Black Adam.

title: Oh, Daisy!
description: Buttercup is not a fan of Bubbles' newly created digital assistant.

title: Block Party
description: Apple and Onion have to outwit a mean duck who's taken over their building's roof.

title: Vecinos
description: Algunos vecinos nuevos arman campamento junto a la cueva de los Osos. A Panda y a Polar les encanta, pero Pardo cree que no tienen buenas intenciones.

title: The Sound and the Furry
description: As Team Tennyson leaves the Frozen Man Festival, Lord Decibel takes center stage to threaten the festival-goers, creating an avalanche if his ransom isn't paid. An over matched Ben must step out of his comfort zone to save the festival from his noisy nemesis!

title: Time Traveling Quick Pants
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn about a quicksand that lets them go back in time.

title: Need for Speed
description: Touring Yellowstone, Ben uncovers a plot by the fast & furious LaGrange to find treasure buried below the national park, but with a little help from Old Faithful, Overflow is able to douse LaGrange's dreams.

title: Gemcation
description: Greg and the Gems take Steven on vacation to help him relax.

title: Fathers and Friends/Midsummer Nightmare
description: Midsummer Nightmare: Drago and the other AO Bakugan face an unseen threat with earth shattering power only to be left wondering if it was all a dream./Father's and Fiends: Osamu Kazami comes to take his son Shun back home and finds a defiance he hadn't counted on.

title: The Curse
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP run afoul of some no-good teenage witches and are cursed! Lousy teenagers!

title: The Mystery of the Timekeeper
description: When the Time Keeper goes missing, Craig and his friends take up the task of helping kids get home in time for dinner.

title: El eslabon mas debil
description: Lloyd le paga con la misma moneda a Harumi para quitarle el poder a su padre, y los Ninjas aprenden lo que se necesita para ser un Cazador de Dragones.

title: Incendium
description: Jake sets Finn up with the Flame Princess - with fiery results.

title: Brains TV
description: After a marathon of classic sitcom episodes, Clarence becomes stuck as alter-ego "Clarry," an obnoxiously overacting sitcom version of himself. It's up to his friends and family to help him snap out of it, or face life with a new Clarence.

title: Pancake's Bus Tour
description: Apple and Onion go on a guided bus tour as part of their plan to get Apple's shoe back.

title: The Galactic Enforcers
description: Ben joins a trio of intergalactic alien heroes tracking down the bounty hunter Six Six. But this bunch of heroes is not all it's cracked up to be.

title: Private Lake
description: When the local lake is overcrowded with tourists, the Bears have fun at Charlie's private lake.

title: Lars de las estrellas
description: Lars demuestra estar a la altura.

title: The Bad Guy Busters
description: Izzy wants to play a superhero game and is willing to do whatever it takes to get the others to see it through.

title: Omni-Tricked
description: Ben's vacation to Portland is cut short when he discovers an 11th alien while battling a Dr. Animo Mega-Creature. But when the fight leaves his Omnitrix on the fritz cycling through all 11 aliens, Max seeks help from an old friend to fix the Omnitrix as other dangerous forces seek it including a mysterious alien that's the same species as the 11th alien, Vilgax!

title: Intravension
description: Los misterios de las Omni-Mejoras se resuelven cuando Ben lucha contra una invasión alienígena proveniente del Omnitrix.

title: Omni-Copped
description: When Grandpa Max's engineer buddy Phil Billings gifts Team Tennyson the Omni-Copter, a state of the art flying vehicle that can transport the Rustbucket for overseas adventures, Steam Smythe takes to the skies to ground Ben and company's first test flight; but unbeknownst to our heroes, Smythe was sent to battle Ben's latest alien forms by a mysterious, powerful enemy: the Forever Knight.

title: La princesa de jade
description: A raíz de un cruel ataque al Palacio, Los Hijos de Garmadon roban la segunda Máscara Oni, y los ninjas invitan a la Princesa Real, Harumi, a su improvisada familia.

title: Made of Honor
description: Steven has a big surprise for the Crystal Gems.

title: Lunch with Tabes
description: When Tabes's lunch gets stolen, Tabes launches a full investigation to find the culprit.

title: Ataque en el Palacio de los Panqueques
description: Cuando Gwen se inscribe en un concurso de comer panqueques en el mundialmente famoso Palacio de los Panqueques, Ben encuentra a los Bugg Bros. y debe detenerlos antes de que puedan obtener una provisión infinita del elemento que les da vida a sus creaciones: los panqueques del Palacio del Panqueque.

title: Ace of Squares
description: Craig vows to make the game of Four Square fun again by challenging its most dominant player!

title: Osos Repartidores
description: Los ositos comienzan a trabajar de repartidores de periódicos.

title: El Favorito de la Profesora
description: Los ositos van a la escuela para escapar de sus vidas agitadas.

title: Dog Decider
description: Unable to make tough decisions, Craig decides to put his choices in the hands of a dog named Fred.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Cluckwork Orange
description: After befriending a chicken with a bad attitude at a petting zoo, Jude is followed back to school by the chicken. He defends the bad bird's behavior until he can defend it no longer.

title: Memory Part 1
description: Windblade tries to help Bumbleebee but he is wary of this "stranger".

title: Omni-Truco
description: Ben debe interrumpir sus vacaciones en Portland cuando descubre un 11mo alien al luchar contra la mega criatura del Dr. Animal. Pero, como la lucha deja a su Omnitrix todo estropeado pasando por los 11 aliens, Max pide ayuda a un viejo amigo para que repare el Omnitrix, que es perseguido por otras fuerzas peligrosas, entre ellas un alien misterioso de la misma especie que el 11mo alien...iVilgax!

title: Tiger Fail
description: Gwen refuses to be pressured into choosing an ice cream flavor that she does not want.

title: The Power Is Yours!
description: A special hero helps Lakewood Plaza Turbo save the planet.

title: Expreso De Gran Estres
description: Durante una transmisión en vivo del nuevo tren bala transcontinental, La Grange se cuela para ganarle al tren. Pero Ben se suma a la diversión, iy no se detendrá ante nada para salir victorioso!

title: Tunnels
description: The Bears discover a network of tunnels underneath the cave. Are they prepared to discover where they lead to and who dug them?

title: Now We're Only Falling Apart
description: Pearl tells a story.

title: Lars of the Stars
description: Lars rises to the occasion.

title: Creek Cart Racers
description: A high-speed race with a high-stakes prize may be too much for Craig and his friends.

title: Pantalones Movedizos del Tiempo
description: Oscar y Erizo se enteran de la existencia de unas arenas movedizas que les permiten viajar en el tiempo.

title: Strange Nedfellows
description: Omnibus hires the Warriors to get a one-of-a-kind salmon for his fancy aquarium, but Neddy joins them on their quest and wants the "Queen Sal," yet Man Fish the Fish Man wants the salmon to stay in the Fickle Sea!

title: Anywhere but Sumo
description: When Clarence realizes Sumo has made a new group of friends at his new school, he becomes jealous and confused. Will Clarence accept a school life void of Sumo, or scheme his way into making their friendship work?

title: Crowbar Jones
description: Pardo proyecta una película amateur épica que acaba de rodar para un grupo focal. Pero cuando se da cuenta de que la gente se marcha, debe descubrir formas de mantener interesada a la audiencia.

title: Game Over
description: When Ben, as Upgrade, and Gwen get zapped into a Sumo Slammers video game, Ben soon has to deal with Gwen's superior gaming skills, while he also tries to impress his video icon in the game.

title: Hotdog's Movie Premiere
description: Apple and Onion square off against a no-nonsense security guard after they're banned from the premiere of their friend Hot Dog's new movie.

title: El chillido de hombre muerto
description: La casi desaparición de Zane a manos del Señor "E" obliga a los ninjas a huir a bordo del Bounty, donde descubren que una tramisión que Zane interceptó puede revelar la ubicación oculta del "Silencioso".

title: Just Wait in the Car
description: As Mary runs errands, Clarence waits in the car and struggles to fight boredom.

title: Cambia de Parecer
description: Steven se enfrenta al mayor desafío de su vida.

title: Elevando el granero
description: iCalabaza desaparece!

title: Speed Demon/Mojo Jonesin'
description: Mojo Jonesin':  When the children of Pokey Oaks become envious of the girls' superpowers, a mysterious figure offers them Chemical X. Now, the girls must fight their own classmates who have powers equal to their own./Speed Demon: The girls accidentally fly at the speed of light and when they arrive home, everything has changed. Fifty years have passed and the world has been taken over by Him.

title: Gilben's Different
description: Gilben's newly sprouted peach fuzz sparks a discussion about puberty that ultimately convinces Clarence to act more like an adult.

title: RC Car
description: Clarence spends a day outside with his toy RC Car, which he names Carla. Eventually convinced Carla has a mind of her own, he decides to follow her to new adventures. Will Clarence's car chase get in the way of Jeff and Sumo's plans for the day?

title: The Brood
description: Craig's determination to get his granddad a cicada shell causes him, Kelsey and JP to become trapped in their stump!

title: Sharing Is Caring
description: Courtney refuses to share her valuable collectors item toy with her classmates.

title: A Single Pale Rose
description: Steven helps Pearl find her phone.

title: Letters to Lars
description: Steven writes about the latest news of Beach City.

title: Summer Love
description: Panda goes on a mission to return a lost phone to the girl of his dreams.

title: Planet Bears
description: A nature documentary follows the Bears through their normal routine, which includes a trip to the grocery store.

title: Dewey gana
description: Steven ayuda al alcalde Dewey a llevar adelante una campaña difícil.

title: Tips
description: Apple and Onion have to find a way to ride the Hot Air Balloon which is in their town for one day only.

title: Hole in 10
description: While mini-golfing, Ben is attacked by the Ground Hawgs, a gang of Dr. Animo mutants turned bikers. When the Hawgs realize the faux mini-golf village isn't an actual town, Ben must go alien to stop them before they set their sights on the real city down the road.

title: Nuggets de Pollo de Sabiduria
description: Cuando Ben y Max comienzan a discutir, Ben se convierte en Fuego para desahogarse, contra la voluntad de Max. Pero una vez que el Dr. Animo lo ve y convierte a Max en un pollo, Ben debe enmendar su error si quiere salvar a su Abuelo y detener al Dr. Animo.

title: Legs from Here to Homeworld
description: Steven travels to visit family.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: The 11th Alien Part 1
description: With new Omni-Enhancements in tow, Ben looks to save a town from a sudden mudslide, but his heroics are short lived once Vilgax appears to warn our hero about the consequences of the Omnitrix's mysterious new alien.

title: El pie grande de Charlie
description: Cuando Charlie se lastima el pie, los Osos tienen que meterlo en un hospital sin que los vean para que reciba atención médica.

title: Xingo
description: Ben está muy interesado en una maratón de Spazz, su dibujo animado favorito, pero cuando se transforma en Upgrade para mejorar la señal de televisión, el protagonista de Spazz salta de su dimensión animada hacia la nuestra...iy trae consigo un caos demente!

title: Monster Visit
description: The monsters get nervous when their Godmonster comes for a visit.

title: A Fistful of Brains
description: Grandpa Max and Rook are looking all over the galaxy for Ben, who is trapped on Khyber's hidden personal hunting preserve.

title: Buen Viaje
description: Abordo del SS Pettigrew en su último viaje, Ben debe luchar no solo contra el mareo sino también contra Vapor Smythe, que se propone usar a sus criaturas mecánicas para hundir el barco moderno que remplaza al vapor... iy a sus pasajeros!

title: Safari Sa'Bad
description: On their trip to Adrenaworld West, Ben takes a detour on a jungle cruise and finds himself hunted by the evil Tim Buktu. Our hero must outwit the baddie if he wants to make it off the amusement park ride alive!

title: El Relopulpo
description: En una pacífica ciudad costera, Ben no solo debe enfrentarse a Vapor Smythe -su arcaico antagonista- y a su última creación, el Relopulpo... isino que también debe enfrentarse a su temor más profundo y oscuro: los calamares!

title: Luces Brillantes, Corazones Oscuros
description: Ben, Gwen y Max hacen una parada en el cementerio falso en el que se filma el programa de televisión favorito de Gwen, pero cuando Ben descubre que su protagonista, Michael Morningstar, es un vampiro de la energía, se transforma en alienígena para mostrarle al mundo quién es la verdadera estrella del programa: Fuego.

title: Teletraan X Part 2
description: Investigating a signal in an abandoned missile silo, Bee and Windblade discover their computer back up drone Teletraan X, but it's a trap!

title: El gran espectaculo
description: Steven filma un documental que sigue los pasos de una banda local mientras consiguen su primer gran oportunidad.

title: La Desaparicion de la Manta de Peper
description: La manta de Pepper desaparece en una pijamada en la cabaña.

title: La ofensiva de Encantos
description: Cuando Ben recibe demasiada publicidad por sus travesuras alienígenas en Fort Knox, Gwen se pone celosa, se siente poco apreciada, y busca aliviar su dolor con helado. Pero cuando Charmcaster la confronta con la intención de vengar a Michael Morningstar, Gwen debe demostrarse a sí misma que es un miembro digno del equipo Tennyson si quiere sobrevivir.

title: Salsa Picante
description: La búsqueda de su salsa picante favorita hace que los Osos se involucren en una operación de picadura.

title: El viaje
description: Chloe y los osos hacen un viaje en auto para ver una lluvia de meteoritos. Polar, el único que tiene licencia de conducir, está a cargo del manejo, lo cual se vuelve más difícil de lo que pensaba.

title: Necesidad De Velocidad
description: De paseo por Yellowstone, Ben descubre el plan del rápido y furioso LaGrange para encontrar un tesoro enterrado bajo el parque nacional. Pero con una ayudita del géiser Viejo Fiel, Overflow logra empapar los sueños de LaGrange.

title: Conduciendo A La Locura
description: Cuando la Chatarra se rompe en un parque de casas rodantes, Ben descubre que se encuentran en la última etapa del Cali 10 Hundred-una carrera de autos épica todo terreno-en la que LaGrange, el piloto demente, ha regresado en busca de venganza contra aquellos que lo descalificaron hace años.

title: Una sola rosa palida
description: Steven ayuda a Perla a encontrar su teléfono.

title: J-Pony
description: JP decide seguir su corazón y trata de unirse a las Chicas Ecuestres.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Dance Lessons
description: Panda volunteers to be Lucy's partner for a dance contest. But Panda doesn't have the heart to tell Lucy that she's a terrible dancer.

title: Game of Masks
description: As Lloyd and Harumi search the Oni Temple for the last mask, the ninja are taken hostage and discover Princess Harumi's true intentions.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 1
description: With Windblade captured by the Seekers, Bumblebee is on his own for the first time and is responsible for saving Cybertron.

title: The Hands of Time
description: Master Wu mistakenly tries to single-handedly complete a battle he began decades ago against Acronix, one of the twin Hands of Time. But the arrival of the first Time Blade, a weapon with the power to speed up time, sends the Ninja to the Monastery just in time to rescue their master from certain doom.

title: Campeon del Cuadro
description: iCraig promete hacer que el juego de Cuatro Cuadros vuelva a ser divertido cuando desafía a su jugador más experto!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Zombozo-Land
description: Ben, Gwen and Max revisit their favorite amusement park, renovated and re-branded as AdrenaWORLD! Unfortunately, the new management is Zombozo and his trio of new henchmen! He's got a plan to hypnotize everyone in the park to form a criminal army. Ben has to set aside his desire to ride every ride in the park and make things right.

title: Paint That a Shame
description: Leshawna creates a paint balloon fight to decide who gets to come with her to an amusement park.

title: The Heist
description: Richard discovers going into a bank whilst wearing a motorcycle helmet can land you in a lot of trouble.

title: El arte de panda
description: Panda pinta un retrato de Charlie que se vuelve un éxito en su clase de arte. Pero cuando un marchante ofrece comprar la pintura, Panda tiene que lograr que Charlie se la devuelva.

title: Xingo
description: Ben is more interested in a marathon of his favorite cartoon show, "Xingo", but when Ben goes Upgrade to get a better signal, the titular Xingo leaps from his animated dimension to ours, bringing mad chaos with him!

title: Visita Monstruosa
description: Los monstruos se ponen nerviosos cuando su Dios monstruo llega de visita.

title: True Potential
description: Just when the Ninja think they have saved the day, Lord Garmadon returns to Ninjago, and frees Harumi, who encourages him to "achieve his true potential" by conquering the one thing that has always stood in his way, his son, Lloyd.

title: Ralph
description: Charlie meets a creature just like him named Ralph. Charlie loves having a new friend, but the Bears think Ralph is bad news.

title: Innervasion Part 3: Strange Bedfellows
description: After the Junkbot shoots the Omnitrix and it begins glowing neon-blue, an imprisoned Vilgax explains it is now a gateway through which the Fulmini Empire will invade Earth, but the only way to stop them is from within the Omnitrix, so Ben must team up with the ultimate baddie if he is to save his planet.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Panda's Art
description: Panda paints a portrait of Charlie and it's a hit with his art class. But after an art dealer offers to buy the painting, Panda has to get it back from Charlie.

title: Charm School's Out
description: During a family cookout at a forest campsite, Charmcaster users her magic to switch places with Gwen, but when Ben catches "Charmcaster" sneaking about, he attacks, unaware it's actually his cursed cousin!

title: A Licking Time Bomb
description: Owen and Noah unwittingly become cookie moguls and must hide the secret ingredient, which is Owen's spit from licking the sprinkles off the cookies.

title: Artesanias traviesas
description: Cuando, por accidente, Vic libera al señor de las travesuras del interior una reliquia antigua, V y V tienen que trabajar en equipo para volver a encerrarlo.

title: Animal Day
description: Clarence feels the call of the wild - and decides to live a new life, free of the hustle and bustle of the modern world. Recruiting a few friends, Clarence sets out to find a new place to live his feral life, but quickly realizes he lacks some basic survival skills.

title: Villain Time
description: Ben must go alien to save the Hoover Dam from disaster, but when tough guy hero Tim Buktu swoops in to "help", Ben must figure out if Tim is friend… or foe.

title: Bad Man Oldman
description: When the Warriors re-thatch Old Man Oldman's roof and absentmindedly make it look like Prohyas' hair, Oldman dons an giant evil toupee exacts his revenge!

title: Despeguemos
description: De excursión en Cabo Cañaveral, el trío Tennyson presencia el lanzamiento inaugural de una nave espacial experimental, pero cuando Vilgax comanda la nave, Ben debe impedir que el villano use el transbordador como arma antes de que la cuenta regresiva llegue a cero.

title: Waterfilter
description: Ben, Gwen, and Max's trip to Niagara Falls is cut short by the horrid Hydromanders, creatures menacing them and their fellow tourists.

title: Half-Sies
description: During a trip to the Lake of the Ozarks, Ben and Gwen squabble over Ben's unnecessary "half-birthday" celebration, but when Max gets word of a suspicious rockslide nearby, the cousins must put aside their differences if they are to rescue the trapped miners and uncover who is behind the manmade catastrophe before it's too late: the Bugg Brothers.

title: Lazer Royale
description: The Baby Bears sign up for a game of laser tag, hoping to win some ice cream. But, the round of laser tag turns out to be less of a game and more like a war zone.

title: Ben 24hrs
description: When Ben (and Gwen!) attempt to stay up all night for Adrenaland, the only theme park open 24/7, he not only fails to utilize his alien powers to stay awake, but his "sleep-alien-ing" causes disaster after disaster that Gwen must fix before things get way out of hand.

title: Atrapados juntos
description: Steven y Lars pasan algo de tiempo juntos.

title: Part 7 - Beasts and Dragons
description: Jay, Kai and Zane remember some of Ninjago's most fearsome creatures in order to help Cole defend the cave from an unidentified monster.

title: Stay Goth, Poodle Girl, Stay Goth
description: Gwen accidentally brings a pink stuffed pony she loves to daycare and spends the day denying it's hers.

title: Double Hex
description: While bird watching at Pinnacles National Park, Gwen and Ben get into a competition of who can spot more birds first, but once a forest fire interrupts their fun, Team Tennyson must hurry if they are to save the bird population and discover who is behind the suspiciously growing fire: Hex!

title: Ganas de Explorar
description: La misión de Craig de mapear el Arroyo entero los lleva a él y a sus amigos a arboleda traicionera de Hiedra Venenosa
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Cronicas de Mentiras Basquetboleras
description: Con la ayuda de Basketball, Oscar hace un tiro impresionante que le permite conseguir un lugar en la Liga Dorada.

title: Vote Zombozo!
description: When the Rustbucket must tune-up in the same town as Zombozo's latest campaign trail stop, Ben soon discovers the clown is using his speeches to hypnotize then rob the town, and Team Tennyson must stop the baddie from winning the election.

title: El Onceavo Alienigena Parte 1
description: Con sus nuevas Omni-Mejoras, Ben intenta salvar una ciudad de un repentino alud. Pero su heroísmo dura poco, porque llega Vilgax a advertirlo de las consecuencias del misterioso alien del Omnitrix.

title: Whiteout Part 2
description: Windblade flies to the Himalayas to investigate while Bee watches television, acquiring new verbal "samples".

title: Brief Career of Lucky Girl
description: When a wizard cos player gets his hands on a real, magical wand at Comic Con, Ben enlists Gwen to help stop Hex from retrieving it by tricking the wicked warlock into thinking she is a powerful magic-wielder in her own right: the one and only Lucky Girl!

title: The Demon
description: Chloe and Ice Bear accidentally lose Chloe's prized hoodie to the ferocious dog next store. They go on a mission to get it back.

title: 4 on 1
description: Onion's fear of crowds threatens his basketball team's success.

title: Fire!
description: Grizz's quick thinking prevents a potential wild fire, but the praise he receives from doing so quickly goes to his head.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Escape from Family Dinner
description: There's a huge water balloon fight at the creek but Craig is stuck at home for a family dinner, unless he can escape.

title: The Takeout Mission
description: Kelsey leads her friends on the most important quest ever, picking up takeout for dinner.

title: Videodrone
description: Mega Man must stop Hypno Woman from turning the students and teachers at Silicon Central into her mindless drones.

title: Ice Cave
description: Ralph takes over the cave and turns it into a snowy fortress where he reigns as king over the Bears and Charlie.

title: Steam is the Word
description: In the heart of Silicon Valley, Ben has to stop Victorian villain Steam Smythe from securing an epic power source sealed in a Tesla time capsule.

title: Max Al Maximo
description: Mientras Ben, Gwen y Max van de excursión a una cascada, los Hermanos Bugg regresan con el plan de duplicar a Diamante. Pero cuando su arma láser clonadora le dispara a Max por error-y lo multiplica infinitamente-, Gwen y Ben deben juntar a todos los Maxes y ahuyentar a los Hermanos Bugg a la vez.

title: Jungle Moon
description: Stevonnie finds themself alone on an adventure.

title: Hot Dog estrena su pelicula
description: Cuando unos guardias de seguridad muy serios los echan del estreno de la nueva película de su amigo Hot Dog, Manzana y Cebollín se preparan para pelear.

title: Vacaciones
description: El doctor de Nom Nom le ordena tomarse unas vacaciones. Pero debe viajar con un compañero incompatible con él: Pardo.

title: I Used to Be a Peoples
description: Robin feels the other Titans are spending too much time together so he encourages them to spend some time alone.

title: Mayhem in Mascot
description: After their attempt to get a photo with every storefront mascot is foiled, Ben and Gwen sneak out at night to get their photo with the wooden bear totem known as "Yawk", only to find he and the other mascots have come to life!

title: Chadsgiving
description: Clarence is excited for Thanksgiving Dinner with Chad's parents, but Chad is worried that their unusually laid back demeanor and bizarre customs will make him look irresponsible by association.

title: Todo Mojado
description: Nadie le cree a Ben cuando insiste en que uno de los demás clientes que aguarda en la fila del parque acuático es la malvada Frightwig disfrazada de niña común. Por eso, Ben debe demostrar que dice la verdad mientras protege a los asistentes al parque del plan maestro de la villana: idestruir el parque con su propia presión acuática!

title: Innervasion Part 4: Mind over Alien Matter
description: While inside the Omnitrix, Ben and Vilgax must work together if they are to close the gateway, but once the Fulmini leader, the High Override, appears, even that might not be enough. Luckily, help arrives in the form of a being calling itself Glitch!

title: Pepper's Blanket Is Missing
description: Pepper's blanket goes missing at a cabin sleepover.

title: Show Don't Tell
description: Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max arrive at a Native American national park to witness the Ayasha Plinths, an ancient Stonehenge-like rock formation. But when the sinister sorcerer Hex arrives, Ben must battle against a beast Hex magically made out of huge rocks!

title: Panda 2
description: Baby Panda happily lives in a closed off environment for study. But when he's given a new friend, Panda 2, his worldview is shaken, which sets him off on a great adventure.

title: Folk Art Foes
description: When Vic accidently unleashes the lord of mischief from an ancient relic, V and V have to work together to trap it back inside.

title: Hot Sauce
description: A quest for their favorite hot sauce causes the Bears to get involved with a sting operation.

title: Dog Hotel
description: With no place to stay while their cave gets fumigated, the Bears book a night at a hotel for dogs.

title: Silent Treatment/Sweet 'n' Sour
description: The Silent Treatment: When the girls go to see a silent movie with the Professor, they end up getting pulled into the film by an old-time villain./Sweet 'n' Sour: The girls must figure out how to beat Townsville's newest band of criminals: a group of adorable little animals.

title: Part 9 - Prophecy of the Green Ninja
description: The final puzzle forces each ninja to question the true meaning of the Green Ninja Prophecy, but success is not what it seems.

title: Poles Apart
description: A trip to the South Pole goes upside down when Team Tennyson lands on the North Pole instead, but Ben quickly discovers the culprits: Solar & Polar Twain, magnetically-powered scientists who want to hold the world ransom by threatening to reverse Earth's magnetic poles!

title: OTTO Motive
description: Kevin and Rook run into an old enemy from the Null Void while attending an intergalactic auto show. (Re-introducing classic Ben alien, Upgrade.)

title: Ben Again and Again
description: After Billy Billions' efforts to carve his face onto Mount Rushmore with a laser are thwarted by Ben, the billionaire brat turns his focus on removing Ben from the Omnitrix, but once he accidentally rips open a rift in space-time, the two must carefully navigate another timeline if they are to return to the present.

title: El gatito
description: Luego de un percance en el bosque, los Osos pierden su hogar en manos de unos animales peligrosos.

title: Adventures in Babysitting
description: Ben, Gwen, and Max meet a family that appears to be a mirror image of them, but when Max goes off on a hike with their matriarch, Maxine, Ben is forced to babysit Simon Sez, a brat with a Billy Billions designed backpack  that turns him into a formidable robot.

title: The Perfect Tree
description: Chloe and Ice Bear drive up north to find the perfect Christmas tree. Meanwhile, Grizz and Panda are in charge of decorating Chloe's house.

title: Fuzzy Pink Time Babies
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn how to stop time.

title: Ruidosos y Peludos
description: Cuando los Tennyson se van del Festival Frozen Man, Lord Decibel ocupa el escenario central para amenazar a los asistentes y crear una avalancha si no pagan el rescate que pide. iBen se ve superado por su rival y debe salir de su zona de confort para salvar al festival de su entrometido enemigo!

title: Doorway to Helen
description: Craig makes a long distance connection with a kid that loves the creek as much as he does.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Recipe for Disaster
description: During Chefapalooza in the Rocky Mountains, three famous chefs and infamous bad-guys, The Tri-Chefta, hunt down Wildvine in hopes of creating their most exotic dish to date.

title: Blast Resort
description: Mega Man must assist Blasto Woman in a heist to stop a powerful EMP emitter from falling into the wrong hands.

title: Punos Fuertes
description: Harto de perder cuando juega a los videojuegos contra su padre, Craig busca entrenarse en el Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: De laguna en laguna
description: Garnet y Steven exploran las líneas de tiempo más improbables de Ciudad Playa.

title: All Koiled Up
description: When Ben grows impatient with the snail like pace of gardening, he goes O-E Overflow to pick up the pace and accidentally floods the community garden, but once a giant sink hole appears and frees King Koil and his Kimodo Dragon from below, Ben must quickly right his wrong and capture the baddies if he is to save the coastal city of Bayburgh.

title: Dead Man's Squall
description: Zane's near demise at the hands of Mr. E forces the ninja to flee aboard the Bounty, where they discover that a transmission Zane intercepted may reveal the hidden location of the Quiet One.

title: El sentimiento
description: Mientras Max y Gwen se deleitan en el espíritu navideño de Winter Wonderland, Ben no podría estar más aburrido y concentrado en los juguetes. Pero cuando los Weatherheads fijan sus miras en Winter Wonderland como su próximo objetivo, nuestro héroe debe conectarse con sus emociones si quiere salvar la ciudad.

title: Subterranean Homesick Blues/Honey Struck
description: Subterranean Homesick Blues: The AO return home to learn that no time has passed but they soon discover their knowledge of brawling has gotten years more advanced./Honey Struck: After Strata is sent packing the AO discover that they have picked up a hitchhiker a Panda-like Bakugan who is nothing but sticky trouble.

title: The Fair
description: The Baby Bears make a deal with a carnival worker to be prizes for a game of ball toss.

title: Part 6 - The Elemental Masters
description: A riddle requires the Ninja to consider the powers and history of the Elemental Masters. Meanwhile, Nya struggles to keep the power on in the Samurai X Cave.

title: Superfriends
description: The new girl next door learns it's hard to be best friends with superheroes and soon starts hanging out with the wrong kind of kid, Princess.

title: Evicted!
description: Marceline shows up and informs that the tree fort was once hers and she wants it back.

title: Una epoca de traidores
description: Lloyd lucha con su papel como maestro en entrenamiento y Nya hace todo lo posible para reiniciar a Zane.

title: Olvideti
description: Ben, Gwen y Max van de excursión en busca de un Forgeti legendario, un yeti que hace que las personas se olviden de que lo vieron, pero cuando el Doctor Ánimo reúne a los Forgeti para su plan de robar bancos sin que nadie los recuerde, Ben aprende muy pronto que el Forgeti es más que un simple mito.

title: Trampoline
description: Mary buys a new trampoline for the family, but an accident lands her on the couch for a while. Determined to fight the boredom of being stuck indoors, she discovers her neighbor may be hiding something exciting.

title: Can't Go Back
description: Ronaldo spots something mysterious on the moon, and Steven goes to investigate.

title: Assault on Pancake Palace
description: When Gwen enters a pancake eating contest at the world famous Pancake Palace, Ben finds the Bugg Bros. and must stop them before they obtain an endless supply of what fuels their creations: Pancake Palace pancakes.

title: Cortando Camino
description: Ben habla con Geezer Bob para hacer alguna tarea de jardín y así ganar un poco de dinero, pero cuando Ben se transforma en Upgrade para convertir la podadora de césped en una cortadora súper rápida, por accidente despierta la ira de los vecinos gnomos de Bob: los diminutos y aterradoramente obstinados duendes de Billy Bob.

title: Spa Day
description: The Bears have a relaxing day at the spa. Grizz tries to get everything the spa has to offer. Panda gets trapped in the steam room with an old man. And Ice Bear plays ping pong.

title: Cual es tu problema
description: Amatista convence a Steven de que se tome un día libre.

title: Escape de la Cena Familiar
description: En el arroyo se disputa una enorme pelea con globos acuáticos, pero Craig está atrapado en la cena familiar, a menos que pueda escapar.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Story, Bored
description: During a book signing at a medieval castle, Ben must stop Hex from getting his hands on a grimoire that can fuse its user with mythical beasts, creating monstrous hybrids!

title: El Arbol Perfecto
description: Chloe y Polar conducen hacia el norte para encontrar el árbol de Navidad perfecto. Mientras tanto, Pardo y Panda quedan a cargo de la decoración de la casa de Chloe.

title: Selva lunar
description: Stevonnie se encuentra solo en una aventura.

title: La Camada
description: La determinación de Craig de conseguirle a su abuelo un caparazón de cigarra hace que él, Kelsey y JP queden atrapados en su tronco.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: El silencioso
description: Mientras que Lloyd y Harumi se aventuran a lo profundo de "Primeval's Eye" en busca de la tercer máscara Oni, los ninja tratan de arreglar al Bounty y hacer un descubrimiento sorprendente.

title: Computer Vampire
description: Oscar finds a mysterious old video game in the library.

title: The Weakest Link
description: Lloyd turns the tables on Harumi to take his father's power away, and the Ninja learn what it takes to be a Dragon Hunter.

title: Feeling Spacey
description: Oscar and Hedgehog arrive on a planet that has no emotions.

title: Nickname
description: When a kid wants a cool nickname, UG tells him he has to earn it in the most legendary way ever: yard work!

title: Almuerzo con Tabes
description: Cuando alguien se roba el almuerzo de Tabes, él organiza una investigación a fondo para hallar al culpable.

title: Dama de honor
description: Steven tiene una gran sorpresa para las Gemas de Cristal.

title: Dibs Court
description: When a kid claims dibs on the Stump, Craig has no choice but to take them to court. Dibs Court.

title: Missing Cat
description: When Chelsea accidentally lets her pet cat Crumbles out, the cat goes missing! Reluctant to ask for help, she struggles to find the cat before anyone realizes it's gone. It's up to cat whisperer Clarence to interject and find Crumbles, whether Chelsea wants his help or not!

title: #SweetJustice Part 3
description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

title: Ropa Dominguera
description: JP ensucia su última ropa limpia y debe ponerse su mejor ropa de domingo para ir al arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Que No Pare La Musica
description: Ben y Gwen están entusiasmados por ir al concierto de EDM en el Día de la Tierra en Portland, hasta que Lord Decibel, el villano que manipula el sonido, se apodera del concierto cuando intenta usar el sonido como un arma para destruir el planeta.

title: Sabotage Part 2
description: Shockwave creates false memories designed to convince Bee he was always a Decepticon spy.

title: Hora De Ser Villano
description: Ben debe transformarse en alienígena para evitar un desastre en la represa Hoover, pero cuando Tim Buktu, el heroico tipo rudo, se precipita para ayudar, Ben debe descubrir si Tim es su amigo...o su enemigo.

title: Nido de buitres
description: Craig y sus amigos forman una banda, pero a Craig lo atormenta una pesadilla aterradora.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Lago privado
description: Cuando el lago de la zona está repleto de turistas, los Osos se divierten en el lago privado de Charlie.

title: Dia de Spa
description: Los Osos se relajan en el spa. Grizz intenta usar todos los servicios del spa. Panda queda atrapado en la sala de vapor con un anciano. Y Polar juega al ping pong.

title: Planeta osos
description: Un documental sobre la naturaleza sigue a los Osos durante su rutina normal, que incluye un viaje a la tienda de comestibles.

title: Go Fish
description: While on a fishing trip, the Bears get attacked by a giant legendary fish.

title: Cone in 60 Seconds
description: After Owen gets ripped off at the ice cream truck, the kids unite to right that wrong.

title: All Wet
description: No one believes Ben when he insists that one of the other patrons waiting in line at the World of Wet Water Park is the nefarious Frightwig disguised as a common girl. So Ben must prove his case while protecting park goers from her master plan: to destroy the park with its own water pressure!

title: Una linea en la arena
description: Jay lucha por defender la casa de su familia.

title: El Libro Final
description: El último libro de fantasía de la serie favorita de Kelsey desaparece de la biblioteca. Por eso, Craig decide ayudarla a resolver el misterio de quién se lo llevó.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The First Day
description: Best friends Oscar and Hedgehog get dropped off at their first day at summer camp.

title: Enemy of My Enemy
description: When Optimus returns with old friends and dire warnings of a Cybertronian invasion of Earth, the Autobots must split up to defend their old home and their new one, with the Bee Team returning to Cybertron, while Optimus and his All-Stars stay behind to defend against the invasion's advanced force.

title: Under the Overpass
description: Craig and his friends travel to find honeysuckle in the creek but discover a whole new part of the creek.

title: Ranger Norm
description: When Tabes leaves for a conference, the Bears have to deal with her substitute, Ranger Norm.

title: Teletraan X Part 1
description: The Decepticon Armada is nearing Earth to seek the Allspark and are desperate for clues.

title: Apple's in Trouble
description: Apple is challenged to a fight by a grumpy Cheesesteak, so he and Onion go on a quest to find the source of Cheesesteak's grumpiness.

title: Part 10 - Greatest Battles
description: Solving the puzzles releases a new peril for the Ninja to face. Will memories of their greatest victories be enough to defeat it?

title: El Lider Del Ring
description: Cuando Ben tiene una racha ganadora en un videojuego, se le ocurre una idea para ganar un partido real de lucha, hasta que un luchador intimidante decide convertirlo en un verdadero desafío.

title: Charlie's Halloween Thing 2
description: Charlie tells some scary stories featuring the Bears and their friends.

title: Road Trip
description: Chloe and the Bears take a road trip to see a meteor shower. Ice Bear, the only one licensed to drive, is put in charge, which becomes harder than he thought.

title: The Filth
description: Ben is tasked with cleaning the Rust Bucket. But when he is tricked into letting the villainous and vile Fly Guys steal it, he must chase them down before they create an unstoppable maggot monster with sights firmly set on destroying Las Vegas.

title: Esto llega hasta el Once
description: Durante una última parada en una juguetería antes del viaje inaugural de Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max a través del Atlántico, Ben se encuentra con su antiguo bravucón, Kevin 11, que ahora tiene nuevos poderes. Es capaz de transformarse en alienígenas al igual que Ben, como el doble "pirata" de Cannonbolt: iWreckingbolt!

title: Rath of Con
description: Back stateside, Ben can't get into a cat cosplay competition, Top Tail, without a costume of his own; but when he goes Rath, a new cat-like alien with an attitude, Ben's newfound wild side quickly becomes much more than he bargained for.
The Baby Bears' dreams come true when they find a 100 dollar bill. But when they can't bear to spend it, they realize it's difficult to let go.

title: Monstruos Bebes
description: Alice tienta a Oscar y a sus amigos monstruos para que asistan a un té festivo, pero el objetivo real es convertir a los monstruos en tiernos bebés.

title: Snake Jaguar
description: In order to join the Sons of Garmadon, Zane (aka Snake Jaguar) participates in a deadly motorcycle initiation race.

title: Googs
description: The Bears win a tour of the infamous Googs corporate headquarters.

title: Firstbourne
description: Emperor Garmadon has taken control of Ninjago City where Lloyd retreats to the shadows. Meanwhile, the other Ninja and Young Wu are shipwrecked in the Realm of Oni & Dragon and find they are not alone.

title: Ninjago chico, problemas grandes
description: Los ninjas corres a salvar a Lloyd. Un Lord Garmadon más poderoso que nunca, crea una enorme estatua para ayudarlo a gobernar Ninjago y a derrotar a los ninjas.

title: Follow that Space Cab!
description: While Superman escorts his prisoner Mr. Mind between planets, he is attacked by Lobo who wants to collect a reward on Mind. Temporarily powered-down, Superman seeks Space Cabbie's help to get away from Lobo.

title: El Oso
description: In a flashback to long ago, Charlie has an adventure in the Mexican desert.

title: Bright Lights, Black Hearts
description: Ben, Gwen, and Max stop by the graveyard set of Gwen's favorite TV show, The Unalivers, but when Ben discovers its lead, Michael Morningstar, is an energy vampire he goes alien to show the world the real star of the show: Heatblast.

title: El amigo de panda
description: Panda usa una aplicación para encontrar a un amigo con el que tenga más cosas en común. Muy pronto, las cosas dan un giro negativo cuando el nuevo amigo se vuelve demasiado posesivo.

title: Imaginary Friend
description: The Baby Bears invent an imaginary friend, but the trouble he causes is all too real.

title: La feria
description: Los Osos bebés hacen un trato con un empleado del parque de atracciones para convertirse en premios de un juego de lanzamiento de pelota.

title: Guar serpiente
description: Para unirse a Los Hijos de Garmadon, Zane (alias Jaguar Serpiente) participa en una carrera de iniciación mortal de motocicletas.

title: JPony
description: JP decides to follow his heart and tries to join the Horse Girls.

title: Night of the Bat
description: Superman and other Justice League members have to battle Batman when he gets possessed by an evil Djinn, Uthool, who is intent on using the JL power core to blow a crack in Earth.

title: The Kid From 3030
description: The kids meet a mysterious kid from the future and try to help him complete his mission.

title: Panda dos
description: Panda bebé es un sujeto de estudio que vive feliz en un ambiente aislado. Pero cuando llega Panda 2, un nuevo amigo, su visión del mundo se sacude, lo cual lo lanza a una gran aventura.

title: Mask of Power/Story Holes
description:
Mask of Power: Philomena Dusk from AAAnimus Corp. hires Magnus and gives him a control implant to bolster the power of his Bakugan to defeat Dan./Story Holes:  
A cryptic call leads the AO in search of a missing Bakugan but they soon realize the call was actually a test from a mysterious benefactor.

title: Ye Olde Laser Duel
description: As team Tennyson admires the efficiency of a super modern train station, Ben is quick to sniff out one of Steam Smythe's robots holding up the line. Once the fed up villain tricks our hero into accepting a duel, the fate of the Omnitrix hangs in the balance and it's up to Ben to set things right.

title: Part 8 - Rise of Garmadon
description: The Ninja confront memories of their greatest villain and ally, Garmadon, before the threat to Zane controls him completely.

title: No lo digas y Hazlo
description: Ben, Gwen y el Abuelo Max llegan a un parque nacional nativo americano para conocer los plintos de Ayasha, una antigua formación rocosa parecida a la de Stonehenge. Pero cuando llega el siniestro hechicero Hex, iBen debe luchar contra una bestia que Hex hizo mágicamente con rocas enormes!

title: Cube Part 2
description: Windblade finds it hard to believe that Bee can't remember his favorite sport, Cube!

title: Stuck Together
description: Steven and Lars spend some time together.

title: Popular Banana Split
description: Hedgehog and Max discover a tiny high school when they are accidentally shrunk by a science experiment.

title: La Melancolia de Oscar y Erizo
description: Susie organiza el concurso anual de talentos, y todos los campistas compiten para ganar.

title: The Extinction Event Part 2
description: Shockwave orders the Seekers to help him create an extinction event and destroy all organic life on the planet.

title: Juego de mascaras
description: Mientras Lloyd y Harumi buscan el templo Oni para la última máscara, los ninjas son tomados como rehenes y descubren que verdaderas intensiones de la Princesa Harumi.

title: Your Mother and Mine
description: Steven takes Garnet to meet some of his new friends.

title: Death Kwon Do-livery
description: Mordecai and Rigby want to help save Death Kwon Do sensei's life.

title: Peludos Bebes Rosas del Tiempo
description: Oscar y Erizo aprenden a detener el tiempo.

title: Animorfosis
description: El trío Tennyson excava fósiles de dinosaurio, pero Ben no sabe que Vilgax y el Dr. Animal se complotaron para robar ADN alien del Omnitrix, pero, una vez extraído el ADN, Vilgax traiciona a su cómplice. Ahora Ben debe aliarse con el malvado doctor si quiere tener la oportunidad de derrotar al gran villano. Pero ¿puede confiar en el Dr. Animal?

title: Saca tu Bestia
description: Craig quiere jugar a un popular juego de cartas, así que decide tomar prestadas las cartas antiguas y valiosas de Bernard.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Officer Moody
description: Pieces of Mr. Reese's past are revealed when his old partner on the police force, Officer Moody, visits Aberdale Elementary.

title: Ben 24 Horas
description: Cuando Ben (iy Gwen!) intenta quedarse despierto toda la noche para ir a Adrenaland -el único parque temático abierto las 24 horas, los siete días de la semana- no solo es incapaz de utilizar sus poderes alienígenas para lograr su objetivo, sino que además su estado de adormecimiento alienígena provoca un desastre tras otro, y Gwen debe arreglar las cosas antes de que todo se salga de control.

title: The Beast Inside
description: Ben, Gwen and Max make a return to Max's alma mater but this time it's no homecoming. Dr. Animo has made a scary transformation and found a way to release the very dangerous animal nature of humans, including Max's life-long friend!

title: Riding the Storm Out
description: Ben and Gwen's camping trip is interrupted by the emotionless Weatherheads (Gust-o, Hail-o, & Shock-o) but a malfunctioning Omnitrix firing out a mishmash of aliens may not be the forecast for success.

title: Etiquette Clarence
description: Clarence submits a short story into a creative writing contest, and he's overjoyed when he learns he's accepted as a finalist! But when Jeff finds out Clarence has to attend a formal dinner, he fixates on transforming the messy Clarence into a proper gentleman.

title: Sabotage Part 1
description: From his lab on Cybertron, Shockwave launches an attack on Bee's most vulnerable place...his memories.

title: Max's Monster
description: Grandpa Max's old Plumber partner, Phil, seeks Max's help to tame the monster within. (Introducing new Ben alien, Buzzshock; Re-introducing old Ben alien, Benvicktor.)

title: Dog King Clarence
description: When Clarence's neighbor Gale recruits him to dog sit for her, he knows it will be a breeze, being the self-proclaimed "Dog King," Clarence knows all there is to know about pups. Nevertheless, Gale's dog proves to be a little more challenging than he expects!

title: El Espantoso Segundo Especial de Halloween de Charlie
description: Charlie cuenta algunas historias de miedo protagonizadas por los Osos y sus amigos.

title: Billy Bajillions
description: In Aspen, Colorado, Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max are on a hike to find the Forgeti, but when they realize they've stumbled upon Billy Billions own "Winter in July" ski resort, Ben must battle Billy, with an assist from the Forgeti itself.

title: Venthalla
description: Owen has his super ball confiscated and locked up in Chef's office. Duncan, seeing an opportunity to get help escaping the daycare, leads an away team into the vents to recover Owen's ball.

title: Fear the Fogg
description: As Max attempts to get Ben and Gwen to the Four Corners Monument before sunset, an ominous fog bank engulfs the roadway and forces Max to drive at a snails pace, but once The Fogg comes to life and attacks the Rust Bucket, Team Tennyson must work together if they are to navigate to safety.

title: Dead Ringer
description: When Vic doesn't pick Val for his soccer team, Val vows to win with his own squad. But when his team doesn't match up, he resorts to supernatural means to win.

title: Googs
description: Los osos ganan un tour a las oficinas de una importante empresa.

title: Chocolate Money Badgers
description: Oscar learns that he can earn merit badges that unlock prizes.

title: #AdventuresInBunnysitting
description: Zee asks Kara to look after her two magical bunnies, which quickly start to multiply, wreaking havoc all across Metropolis.

title: Super-Villain Team-Up
description: After a lull in alien antics, a restless Ben suggests to Max and Gwen that he might be a better hero if he went solo, but once Vilgax enlists the help of Zombozo to build a giant hypno-mechanism to hypnotize the entire world, Ben must rethink his strategy if he is to defeat the super-villain team-up.

title: Sadie asesina
description: Steven y los Chicos Geniales arman una banda, pero les cuesta encontrar un sonido propio.

title: Drone On
description: Ben and Gwen are in a highly competitive paper airplane war, but when alien-tech drones bombard the Rustbucket, the cousins must work together to ground the aerial attack and find out who's behind it: the alien conqueror, Vilgax!

title: The Journey Part 2
description: The Autobots are nearly out of Energon, so they land on a dark planet where they encounter subterranean creatures.

title: Braces
description: When the Bears go to the dentist, Panda gets braces. But, Panda finds out his braces grant him super abilities and the power goes to his head.

title: Siloed Part 1
description: Windblade is playing Cube on Cybertron with Bee when she realizes these are memories and she is still held captive by Slipstream.

title: Cube Part 1
description: Bee discovers a mysterious object in the stolen Decepticon shuttle.

title: Lost in Time
description: Kai and Nya stow away aboard Krux and Acronix's time traveling snake mech in a desperate attempt to save Master Wu. But when they arrive in the past, they must help the Elemental Masters prevent the Hands of Time from literally re-writing NinjaGo history. Meanwhile, the the Ninja remain in the rapidly-shifting present trying to help Kai and Nya's father, who was hit with a Time Punch.

title: Drive You Crazy
description: After the Rust Bucket breaks down at a Mobile Home Park, Ben discovers they've stumbled on to the last leg of the Cali 10 Hundred, an epic, off-road auto race where mad driver Le Grange has returned for revenge against those that disqualified him years ago.

title: Reunited
description: Steven brings everyone together for a special reunion.

title: Intolerancia Heladil
description: Los campistas obtienen poderes mágicos gracias a la reserva de helado mágico de las brujas.

title: Pijamas Pijamas
description: Oscar finge hablar con unos pijamas llamados "Jimjams" para hacer feliz a su amigo Pijama.

title: Muerto De Miedo
description: Cuando la Chatarra se queda sin gasolina en una carretera brumosa de la Costa Este, Ben, Gwen y Max se ven obligados a pasar la noche en un hotel amenazado por Creepy Carl, iun experto en folclore de la zona que podría ser un fantasma verdadero!

title: Bridge Out
description: After an overpass collapses on the highway, Team Tennyson is in a traffic jam along with Simon Sez and family. But when Ben and Simon team up to tackle the gridlock together, Simon only makes matters much, much worse.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: El Parque
description: Los Osos pasan un día en el parque. Pardo hace ejercicio, Panda intenta vender sus obras de arte y Polar entrena a unos niños.

title: Problemas Lunares
description: La Luna se entristece cuando Oscar pierde su brazalete de la amistad.

title: Tubin'
description: In search of some adventure, the Bears ride a tube down a dangerous river.

title: Adopted
description: The Baby Bears get adopted by an eccentric millionaire and get to live in his mansion.

title: Jessica Goes to the Creek
description: When Craig and Jessica are locked out of the house, Craig has no choice but to bring his little sister to the Creek.

title: I, Butler
description: The Bears use a robot bear to help around the house. But things get tricky when they lose control of the robot.

title: Omnicoptero
description: Cuando el ingeniero Phil Billings, amigo del Abuelo Max, le regala al equipo Tennyson el Omni-Copter, un vehículo volador de última generación que puede transportar el Rustbucket hasta aventuras en el extranjero, Vapor Smythe sube a los cielos para obligar a aterrizar el primer vuelo de prueba de Ben y su familia. Pero sin que nuestros héroes lo sepan, Smythe fue enviado a combatir las formas alienígenas más nuevas de Ben por un misterioso y poderoso enemigo: el Caballero por Siempre.

title: El panal
description: Los Osos permiten que unas abejas vivan en la cueva para hacer miel. Pero pronto, los Osos, embelesados por la miel, se convieten en los sirvientes automatizados de las abejas.

title: King of the Dinosaurs Part 1
description: With the help of Teletraan- X, Bee and Windblade excavate an deactivated Autobot that looks like a dinosaur.

title: Kyle
description: Nom Nom se reúne con Kyle, su hermano del que estaba distanciado.

title: Bombazobo Vive
description: Durante un viaje de rutina al DMV, Max toma un examen de manejo para renovar su licencia. Pero cuando Zombozo, disfrazado, se apropia del papel del instructor, Ben se convierte en alienígena para detener al malvado y salvar el viaje familiar.

title: Memories of Bobby
description: When a pillar of the Creek community leaves, our trio mourns their loss by remembering the good times.

title: Presentando a La Creatura
description: Cuando Max se queda dormido antes de una doble función, Ben y Gwen se ven obligados a salvar el autocine solos. Ocurre que el malvado mago Hex da vida al monstruo de una película, que aterroriza a los espectadores.

title: Grup Jam
description: Grup invents the "new" sport of basketball, but the stakes are too high for the Warriors to let him play the Galacton team, as the winner shall rule the Kingdom of Rhyboflaven.

title: Charlie's Halloween Thing
description: Charlie hosts an evening of spooky stories starring the Bears.

title: Professor Lampwick
description: Chloe's professor is too mean to give her any face time to talk over her poor grade. The Bears take things into their own hands to help, causing big trouble for Chloe.

title: Teacher's Pet
description: The Baby Bears escape their hectic lives by attending school.

title: Todo Enrollado
description: Cuando Ben se impacienta con el ritmo lento de la jardinería, se convierte en O-E Overflow para acelerar las cosas y, por accidente, inunda el jardín de la comunidad.

title: Delivery Effect
description: Unikitty and gang have ordered some delicious Thai food for dinner.  Unfortunately the wait for the delivery is proving too much, time itself seems to have slowed down. In an effort to get the food their faster the gang utilizes Dr. Fox's time machine, which causes big problems and really hurts Father Time's feelings.

title: Bajo el Puente
description: Craig y sus amigos viajan para encontrar madreselva en el arroyo, pero descubren una parte completamente nueva del arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Best Bears
description: The Bears must complete their Best-Man duties on the day of Darrell's wedding.

title: El hermano de Lucy
description: Para impresionar a Lucy, Panda se ofrece a ser niñero de su hermano, Clifford. Pero Panda no puede hacerse cargo de Clifford porque el niño es demasiado caro de mantener.

title: La pregunta
description: Steven les muestra a unas gemas citadinas cómo vivían los vaqueros.

title: Inglorious Toddlers
description: Owen fears he's about to lose his BFF Noah to a gifted military school.

title: King Koil
description: Ben and Gwen spend the day volunteering at Repto Ranch and come face to face with King Koil, but need to quickly overcome their fear of snakes if they are to rescue the released critters and defeat the slithery baddie.

title: Bounty Ball
description: While Gwen listens to a lecture on the Transcontinental Railroad, Ben sneaks away to the gift shop. But once the Bounty Hunters appear and corner our hero, Gwen must relay the information she learned on the train and use it to their advantage to help Ben escape.

title: Mister Softbol
description: Susie desafía a los campistas a jugar un partido de softball para librarse de una tarea.

title: Moral Decay/Meet the Beat Alls
description: Moral Decay: When Bubbles loses a tooth, she gets a shiny coin under her pillow the next day. Buttercup sees a gold mine in the mouths of Townsville's criminal element./Meet the Beat Alls: Mojo, Him, Princess and Fuzzy band together to form the Bad Four, a criminal supergroup out to destroy the Powerpuff Girls. Everything is going great until Mojo meets Moko Jono and falls in love.

title: Radio Ninjago libre
description: Lloyd deberá encontrar su voz mientras lidera una pequeña resistencia para capturar las señales de transmisión en Ciudad Ninjago. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, el Barón de Hierro lleva a los Ninjas en una cacería de dragones.

title: Ramen
description: The Baby Bears help a struggling ramen chef perfect her ramen and save her shop.

title: Amapolas
description: La guardabosques Tabes guía a una tropa de muchachas a una expedición en una cueva y lleva a Pardo como experto en cuevas.

title: Beach Heads
description: After traveling to Tampa Beach, Florida, Team Tennyson hopes to get some much-needed rest & relaxation, but the tempests without a temper, the Weatherheads, have other plans that Ben must thwart: to build a new beach base!

title: Yo Mayordomo
description: Los Osos usan un oso robótico que los ayuda con las tareas domésticas. Pero las cosas se complican cuando pierden el control del robot.

title: Xingo's Back
description: Left to entertain himself as Max takes a much deserved nap, Ben stumbles upon a Xingo arcade game and goes OE-Shock Rock to power it up, but when it receives too much juice, Xingo leaps out into the real world and our hero must go toe-to-toe with his favorite cartoon character.

title: You're It
description: A vicious game of tag wreaks havoc on the Creek, claiming Kelsey as the next it.

title: Pool Hopping
description: Garnet and Steven explore the most unlikely timelines in Beach City.

title: Something I Ate
description: Ben, Gwen, and Max go on a tour of the impervious Fort Knox, but when Dr. Animo sicks a hungry ani-mutate on the Fort, Ben must stop it before it gobbles up the nation's monitory standard!

title: Return to Forever
description: The Forever Knights threaten to use a sinister weapon to erase all alien DNA on Earth unless Ben and Rook can stop them.

title: Them Soviet Boys
description: In order to quickly get through their chores and karate lessons, the Titans learn how to montage

title: Rainbow Race
description: Sadness levels have hit an all-time low in Frowntown. In an attempt to cheer up the citizens of the town, Unikitty and the gang load a rainbow into a tanker truck with the intention of releasing it over Frowntown. Now they must avoid the marauding Master Frown in his monster truck, to succeed.

title: Subway
description: The Bears are stranded on a subway platform after missing their train. But while waiting, the Bears are challenged with recovering some lost items.

title: La Traes
description: Un despiadado juego de persecución desata un caos en el Arroyo, y se declara a Kelsey como la próxima perseguidora.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Escapismo
description: Steven usa sus poderes psíquicos para conseguir ayuda.

title: Paperboyz
description: The Baby Bears get jobs as paper boys.

title: El futuro es de Carton
description: Los niños conocen a un excéntrico Creador de Cartón que invita a Craig a ayudarlo a terminar su obra maestra.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Bananas & Cheese
description: Duncan is determined to stop the musical duo Bananas & Cheese from coming to the daycare.

title: Free Chili
description: When Owen hides a walkie-talkie inside his chili dog, Harold believes it's an alien here to destroy Earth.

title: All Up in Your Drill
description: Duncan stages a small coup to oust Courtney as their official class firefighter so that he can wear the shiny firefighter helmet - until he smells smoke in the classroom and begs her to take her job back.

title: Batalla en El Biggie Box
description: Ben y Billy Billions se enfrentan por un set de sumo exclusivo que se vende únicamente en el centro comercial más grande del mundo, isolo para descubrir que Simon Sez, de apenas seis años, lo compró primero! Así se desata una batalla dentro de una tienda que parece tenerlo todo excepto una salida fácil de encontrar.

title: Aventuras Cuidando Ninos
description: Ben, Gwen y Max se encuentran con una familia que parece ser un reflejo de ellos. Pero cuando Max sale a caminar con su matriarca, Maxine, Ben se ve obligado a cuidar a Simon Sez, un malcriado con una mochila diseñada por Billy Billones, que lo convierte en un robot formidable.

title: Pizza Band
description: The Bears get pizza at Papa Bear's Pizza Cave and wind up replacing the place's animatronic band. They're such a hit that they go on tour!

title: Ice Cream Headache
description: The campers get magical powers from the witches supply of magic ice cream.

title: Matrix of Leadership Part 2
description: Bumblebee doubts his abilities as he has to find the Ark to awaken Optimus and the Autobots.

title: The Society
description: Gumball is convinced there is a Secret Society in school and he wants in. Things aren't going Gumball's way at school so he assumes there must be a Secret Society that gives preferential treatment to its own members. He tries everything to uncover this non-existent society, making everyone's lives miserable in the process. Eventually, in an attempt to restore some peace, the pupils and teachers decide to give him exactly what he wants.

title: Chicken Nuggets of Wisdom
description: When Ben and Max get into an argument, Ben goes Heatblast to blow off steam against Max's wishes; but once Dr. Animo spots him and subsequently turns Max into a chicken, it's up to Ben to right his wrong if he is to save his Grandpa and stop Dr. Animo.

title: No puedo regresar
description: Ronaldo divisa algo misterioso en la luna, y Steven sale a investigar.

title: Cueva Helada
description: Ralph se apodera de la cueva y la convierte en una fortaleza nevada, donde reina sobre los Osos y Charlie.

title: The Button
description: The guys have to protect a large red button from being pushed.

title: Noches heladas dos
description: Polar sale a una aventura nocturna para rescatar a Yana, su amiga, de unos enemigos familiares.

title: El chico del 3030
description: Los niños conocen a un misterioso niño del futuro y tratan de ayudarlo a completar su misión.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Together Alone
description: Steven throws a party to bring his family together.

title: Ben una y otra vez
description: Cuando los esfuerzos de Billy Billiones por tallar su cara en el Monte Rushmore con un láser se ven frustrados por Ben, el malcriado multimillonario se concentra en sacar a Ben del Omnitrix. Pero cuando, por accidente, abre una grieta espacio-temporal, ambos deben navegar con cuidado por otra línea de tiempo si quieren regresar al presente.

title: Secrets Discovered
description: Secrets are revealed as Nya confronts the Samurai X imposter, Kai pursues the truth about his parents and the other Ninja desperately seek to locate and rescue Master Wu. But as usual, some answers only lead to more questions.

title: The Mall
description: The Bears go the mall and encounter their human counterparts.

title: Salvajessa
description: Un encuentro con Salvajessa, guardiana de la naturaleza, inspira a Kelsey a dedicarse a una causa.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Rescue Ranger
description: Tabes helps the Bears rescue Charlie after he gets captured by a villainous game hunter.

title: El Show de Nom Nom
description: Las cosas se complican cuando Nom Nom filma su primer programa de televisión. Los Osos se ofrecen a ayudar y aparecen en el programa.

title: A Ninjustice to Harold
